snippet.title: Amber Heard Wears A High-Fashion Swim Cap To The 'Aquaman' Premiere | Access
snippet.description:
Amber Heard dove right in to an unconventional look at the "Aquaman" London premiere! The actress paired her plunging green-and-gold Valentino gown with a swim cap-inspired headpiece that kept her look noticeably on theme. Find out how her co-star Jason Momoa paid playful tribute to the upcoming blockbuster on the red carpet!
